Package commandLineApplication

Class Ship

java.lang.Object
commandLineApplication.Ship
public class Ship
extends java.lang.Object
Ship is the vehicle to travel from an island to the other
There are 4 ships for player to choose from
Author:
Aerinn Nguyen, Bede Skinnier-Vennell
